              "4.1 Description of the event/activity (in English)": "The event is the final webinar of Together for Future VETskills (ToVET) project. It is funded by European Union Erasmus+ KA3 – Support for Policy Reform Networks and Partnerships of Vocational Education and Training (VET).\r\nThe project involves four networks from different parts of Europe. Finnish network European Pathway, Italian networks ENAC ENTE NAZIONALE CANOSSIANO, ENAC and SCUOLA CENTRALE FORMAZIONE ASSOCIAZIONE, SCF and Spanish network IKASLAN. \r\nIn the webinar we share information of the project results as how to build international strategy for a VET provider, to foster innovative learning of key competences in VET and how to take open badges into use.\r\nWe also tell about European Vocational Skills week 2022. \r\n",
