              "4.1 Description of the event/activity (in English)": "The Vocational Training Centre of Kecskemet is holding the Online Career Day for the second time this year for the school leavers. The aim of the event is to help the students enter to the work of life, During the event, the students will get in contact with various companies of the region where they can learn about job opportunities and they can apply for jobs that the companies offer. Prior the event, the students will write CVs and cover letters during lessons with their home-teachers, they will learn about jobsearch and interview types and techniques as well as the rules of online etiquettes. The event will be held in TEAMS application. ",
