              "4.1 Description of the event/activity (in English)": "An exchange student from Turkey is studying at our school this school year. In this context, the foreign language work community organizes an intercultural meeting, to which exchange students of different nationalities studying in the city are also invited. The discussion covers various topics, such as the education system of different countries, the range of vocational training, the admission and examination system. It will also cover general topics such as student agendas, leisure activities, future plans.\r\nIn addition to practice English language, the goal of the program is to introduce our students to different cultures.",
