              "4.1 Description of the event/activity (in English)": "Budapest Center of Technical Vocational Training and its 12 member institutions calls attention for the importance of technical career fields. During the event, the attendee can get to know the vision for the future of technical training. We consider that working together with our schools and partners on sustainability and development of energy production are extremely important, so the focus of our professional education is increasingly transforming to achieve these goals. Furthermore, we have upcoming programs at the event, which provides information about further education for primary school age children - who are about to choose a career - and also for school principals and teachers.",
