              "4.1 Description of the event/activity (in English)": "Our plans for January and February: helping our students in the final classes to fill in the forms of the maturity examination and forms required in higher education, offering the staff up to date information in their career orientation.\r\nOur main programs: \r\n6th of January 2022. a visit of the school managers and a panel of IT colleagues at the University of Neumann Janos in Kecskemet\r\n18th of January 2022 Education day in Balassagyarmat\r\n19th of January 2022 Open doors Day at the University of Neumann Janos\r\n25th of January 2022. an online group interview took place \r\n24th of January – 6th of February 2022 DiabMentor- professional training for techers to support children with diabetes\r\n21st-23rd  February 2022: Career days.",
